
# Images

This folder contains the sample images used to test the OCR application.

## Purpose

These images are processed by the Python script to demonstrate Optical Character Recognition (OCR) using OpenCV and Tesseract OCR.

## Sample Files

- **Note1.jpg** – Sample document containing printed text.
- **Assignment.png** – Sample assignment text for OCR testing.
- **Quote.png** – Motivational quote used to evaluate text extraction.
- **Report.png** – Sample report containing formatted text.

## Supported Image Formats

The application supports the following image formats:

- JPG (.jpg)
- JPEG (.jpeg)
- PNG (.png)
- JFIF (.jfif)

## Note

You can replace these images with your own images for testing. For the best OCR accuracy, use high-resolution images with clear, printed text and good lighting.
